For this challenge, you need to implement a tree component. Lets go.

```vue
<script setup lang="ts">
interface TreeData {
  key: string
  title: string
  children: TreeData[]
}
defineProps<{data: TreeData}>()
</script>

<template>
  <!-- do something.... -->
</template>
```
